  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.4.5">
<l>kalaiyilaṅku makalalkul kamalap pāvai katirmutta veṇṇakaiyāḷ karuṅka ṇāycci</l>
<l>mulaiyilaṅku moḷimaṇippūṇ vaṭamun tēyppa mūvāta varaineṭuntōḷ mūrtti kaṇṭīr</l>
<l>malaiyilaṅku niraiccanti māṭa vīti yāṭavarai maṭamoḻiyār mukatti raṇṭu</l>
<l>cilaivilaṅki maṉañciṟaikoṇ ṭirukkum nāṅkūrt tirutteṟṟi yampalatteṉ ceṅkaṇ mālē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The embodiment with high mountain[-like] shoulders which do not retreat</l>
<l rend="indent">when they scrape against the bright jewels and necklaces</l>
<l rend="indent">shining on the breasts</l>
<l>Of the lotus lady with broad hips where a girdle shimmers, [of] the one</l>
<l rend="indent">with glowing pearl-white teeth, [and of] the dark-eyed herdess, you see,</l>
<l>Is my bright-eyed Māl in Tirutteṟṟiyampalam in Nāṅkūr where,</l>
<l rend="indent">at junctures of streets with rows of mansions that shine [like] mountains,</l>
<l>The two eyebrows arching on the faces of those of naïve speech</l>
<l rend="indent">capture the hearts of young men.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
